341
00:27:30,690 --> 00:27:32,484
How many family members
will you be inviting?

342
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:35,403
No one actually.

343
00:27:35,987 --> 00:27:37,197
Don't you have anyone to invite?

344
00:27:37,947 --> 00:27:40,992
