Confucius' father had Confucius

378
00:29:21,551 --> 00:29:24,471
with a 20-year-old woman

379
00:29:24,596 --> 00:29:26,181
when he was 80.

380
00:29:27,515 --> 00:29:29,934
I heard that children born
to older parents

