412
00:31:24,173 --> 00:31:25,049
Thank you.

413
00:31:28,386 --> 00:31:30,179
-You hang up first.
-Okay.

414
00:31:30,597 --> 00:31:31,472
I'll hang up then.

415
00:32:22,941 --> 00:32:24,484
Mom, I'm home.

416
00:32:28,446 --> 00:32:31,324
My princess.
