452
00:34:41,829 --> 00:34:44,874
Don't lie to my face.
You look so grumpy right now.

453
00:34:45,249 --> 00:34:46,292
I told you.

454
00:34:46,793 --> 00:34:48,211
About Dad getting married,

455
00:34:48,377 --> 00:34:51,047
