around lunchtime tomorrow.

463
00:35:19,367 --> 00:35:20,409
Let's have lunch together.

464
00:35:20,910 --> 00:35:21,911
Sure, no problem.

465
00:35:28,459 --> 00:35:29,752
Oh man...

466
00:35:29,836 --> 00:35:32,088
